# MAINTAINERS

This file lists the maintainers of the OVHcloud TechLabs project.

Maintainers are responsible for:
- Reviewing and merging pull requests
- Managing releases
- Triaging issues
- Setting project direction
- Ensuring code quality and security

## Active Maintainers

### Lead Maintainers
* OVHcloud TechLabs Team
  - GitHub: @ovhcloud/techlabs
  - Responsibilities: Overall project direction, releases, architecture decisions

* Tim Seiffert
  - Email: Tim.Seiffert@ovhcloud.com
  - Responsibilities: Platform development and technical architecture

### Platform Maintainers
* Platform Team
  - Responsibilities: Backend API, infrastructure automation, deployment tools

### Workbooks Maintainers  
* Content Team
  - Responsibilities: Tutorial content, documentation, workshop materials

